references: Repealing: Ord 24746, Ord 30399, Ord 32089, Ord 32540, Ord 34997, Ord 39626, Ord 41405
summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinances Nos. 24746, 30399, 32089, 32540, 34997, 39626 and 41405, respectively creating and establishing certain funds in the City Treasury; describing the source and disposition of funds therein and designating said funds as the "Tubercular Hospital Fund", "Suspense Account Fund", "Bridge Fund", "Lake Burien Railroad Fund", "Garnishment Judgment Fund", "Primary Highway Fund" and "North End Highway Fund".
